American Movie;;90;;94;;R;;In this cult-favorite documentary, Mark Borchardt, an aspiring filmmaker from a working-class Wisconsin background, is set on finishing his low-budget horror movie, despite a barrage of difficulties. Plagued by lack of cash, unreliable help and numerous personal problems, Mark wants to complete the film to raise funds for a more ambitious drama. With the assistance of his bumbling but loyal friend Mike Schank, Mark struggles to move forward, making for plenty of bittersweet moments.;;Documentary;;Chris Smith;;1999;;Mark Borchardt,Tom Schimmels,Monica Borchardt,Alex Borchardt,Chris Borchardt,Ken Keen,Mike Schank,Matt Weisman,Bill Borchardt,Cliff Borchardt,Tom Beach,Joan Petrie,Robert Richard Jorge;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/american_movie